Implemented MCP Sampling provider for delegating LLM calls to host. Added SamplingProvider (src/llm/sampling.rs) implementing LlmProvider trait that uses peer.create_message() via MCP sampling/createMessage protocol. Integrated into RmcpServerHandler with auto-configuration of peer from RequestContext on first tool call. Eliminates need for external API keys when running as MCP server - LLM operations delegate to the host (Claude).